      Check box edit event handler constructor
      Parameters:
      checkBox - Reference to the check box being edited
      oldValue - Previous check box selection state
      newValue - New check box selection state
      fieldOwner - Owner of the data field to which the check box belongs; null if the check box is not a data field
      fieldName - Name of the data field to which the check box belongs; null if the check box is not a data field
